   COVER TEACHERS ARE LOOKING FOR HTLAs TO JOIN OUR AGENCY TO SUPPLY OUR SCHOOLS IN AND AROUND BRISTOL ON A DAY TO DAY OR LONG TERM BASIS!

   With flexible working hours available, teaching assistants looking for either day to day supply on a part or full time basis, or a longer term post are encouraged to apply.

   As a HLTA you will be responsible for delivering pre-planned lessons to classes in KS1 and KS2 covering for teacher PPA or short term absences.

   The ideal candidate will:

   * Hold a HLTA qualification or relevant BA Education/Childcare degree
   * Have previous experience in the same/similar role which can be referenced
   * Have excellent classroom management experience
   * Be committed to high standards of teaching and learning

